Zakari Junior Lambo (ka amụrụ n'ụbọchị nke 19 n'ọnwa Jenụwarị n'afọ 1999) bụ onye egwuregwu bọọlụ nke na-agbara Knokke bọọlụ
A mụrụ ya na Belgium, ọ na-anọchite anya ndị otu mba Niger.
Onye ntorobịa nke Mouscron na Ronse, Lambo malitere ọrụ ya na ọkara-pro n'akụkụ Ronse
Ọ gafere Winkel na 2018, tupu ọ laghachi Ronse n'afọ sochirinụ
Na 5 Eprel 2020, Lambo bịanyere aka na nkwekọrịta afọ abụọ na Knokke.
A mụrụ Lambo na Belgium site na nna Nigerien na nne Burkinabé, ma nwee paspọtụ atọ ahụ
A kpọrọ ya ka ọ nọchite anya ndị otu mba Niger maka egwuregwu enyi na enyi na June 2021. Ya na Niger malitere na mmeri enyi na enyi 2–0 na Gambia na 5 June 2021.
Lambo bụ nwa onye bụbu onye egwuregwu bọọlụ mba Niger bụ Zakari Lambo
